According to Veon's annual report of 2020 LetterOne is the holder of the depositary receipts issued by the  "Stichting Administratiekantoor Mobile Telecommunications Investor" and is therefore entitled to the economic benefits (dividend payments,
other distributions and sale proceeds). Fridman is also 'last_name' for LetterOne, so he is coded to be so for the Stichting as well. However, it is not possible to say who is in charge of the Stichting directly, as the Stichting has no public presence.

column57: The Provincial Court of Luanda, in case no. 3301/2019 - C, dated December 30, 2019, determined the preventive seizure of Vidatel's 25% stake in Unitel. This was approved by a court on the British Virgin Islands (were Vidatel is formally located) who ordered the seizure of all Vidatel ressources in a decision from November 19, 2020. This effectively strips Isabel Dos Santos of her property of Vidatel and places it under escrow arrangement.
